## 30. Concurrency

```v
spawn worker()
```

---

## 31. Async Programming

```v
async func download() {

}

await download()
```

---

## 32. Channels

```v
channel<i32> ch

ch.send(10)

value = ch.recv()
```

---

## 33. Mutex

```v
mutex.lock()

counter++

mutex.unlock()
```

---

## 34. File I/O

```v
