}
```

---

## 39. Attributes

```v
@inline
@packed
@deprecated
```

---

## 40. Compile-Time Execution

```v
comptime {

    generate_enum()
}
```

---

## 41. Reflection

```v
type = typeof(person)

fields = reflect.fields(type)
```

---

## 42. Embedded Systems

Memory-mapped IO:

```v
const GPIOA = 0x40020000

gpio = @ptr<GPIO>(GPIOA)

gpio.out = 1
```

Volatile register:

```v
volatile u32 STATUS
```

Interrupt:

```v
interrupt UART_ISR() {

    handle_uart()
}
```

Bitfield:

```v
bitfield Status {

    ready:1
    error:1
    reserved:6
}
```

